00:30:36.170 --> 00:30:38.209
something went wrong, and
a bud, something we're

00:30:38.209 --> 00:30:39.000
looking forward to.

00:30:39.000 --> 00:30:41.070
So we do it now over
voice recording.

00:30:41.070 --> 00:30:42.366
We text it back and forth.

00:30:42.366 --> 00:30:43.990
But these are all
things we've created,

00:30:43.990 --> 00:30:45.864
