00:30:45.864 --> 00:30:47.400
missing people I love the most.

00:30:47.400 --> 00:30:49.120
And I'm away from
them for weeks.

00:30:49.120 --> 00:30:51.500
So, as a practice,
I'm getting there.

00:30:51.500 --> 00:30:53.126
But it's always a
daily-- it's always

00:30:53.126 --> 00:30:54.375
something I work on every day.

00:30:54.375 --> 00:30:56.320
I'm not uniformly happy.

00:30:56.320 --> 00:30:58.020
I'm not an eternal
optimist who just

00:30:58.020 --> 00:30:59.890
wakes up and flips a switch.

00:30:59.890 --> 00:31:02.780
I do these practices
that I'm recommending.

00:31:02.780 --> 00:31:03.774
I think about them.

00:31:03.774 --> 00:31:04.690
I'm conscious of them.

00:31:04.690 --> 00:31:07.560
I did a meditation this
